Package com.teranpeterson.server.model

Class Event

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.teranpeterson.server.model.Event
  • public class Event
extends java.lang.Object
    Events store information about significant events from a persons life, ie. birth, marriage, death, etc. Each event has a personID that corresponds to a person in the system. The latitude and longitude values are used by the client to map these events.
